So sorry, so sorry about this.

537
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:21,320
It's fine.

538
00:21:21,320 --> 00:21:25,320
Chai, you can go completely
wild and have fun tonight...

539
00:21:25,640 --> 00:21:28,520
just don't bring shame
upon our company, got it?

540
00:21:28,520 --> 00:21:30,040
Understood.

541
00:21:30,040 --> 00:21:31,240
I think for tonight...

542
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:34,120
I'll probably just hook up
with a couple of guys, and that's it.

543
00:21:35,080 --> 00:21:39,280
Oh, hello!
Are you Chai? Hi!

544
00:21:39,680 --> 00:21:40,560
Noy Neung?

545
00:21:40,560 --> 00:21:42,800
Oh, Noy Neung,
you actually know me?

546
00:21:42,800 --> 00:21:43,840
Of course.

547
00:21:43,840 --> 00:21:45,920
I follow your content every single clip.

548
00:21:45,920 --> 00:21:47,160
I'm a huge fan!

549
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:50,480
Oh, thank you so much.

550
00:22:00,640 --> 00:22:03,240
Uh, well, I have to excuse myself first.

551
00:22:03,240 --> 00:22:06,480
I think I just found my target.

552
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:07,480
Oh?

553
00:22:15,720 --> 00:22:17,040
Mr. Gift-Boy, you look...

554
00:22:17,040 --> 00:22:19,400
like your body is
completely rejecting the dancing.

555
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:23,040
Well, I only use my body well
in certain situations.

556
00:22:26,840 --> 00:22:30,560
Shit! Chai! I knew that
asshole would show up.

557
00:22:31,880 --> 00:22:33,000
Are you okay?

558
00:22:33,000 --> 00:22:35,720
I'm, uh...Mr. Ninja...

559
00:22:35,720 --> 00:22:38,720
do you happen to have a spare mask?

560
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:40,680
That black mask guy
is so damn cool.

561
00:22:40,680 --> 00:22:43,960
And that cute Asian look
is totally my vibe.

562
00:22:43,960 --> 00:22:46,280
Why are they wearing masks?

563
00:22:46,280 --> 00:22:49,200
You're so cute,
I really want to see your faces.

564
00:22:49,960 --> 00:22:50,920
Oh!

565
00:22:51,040 --> 00:22:53,960
Aren't you that Charmer Chai?

566
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:56,760
I heard you never miss a single
target you set your eyes on.

567
00:22:58,320 --> 00:22:59,960
I'd love for you to
work your magic on me.

568
00:22:59,960 --> 00:23:03,000
I just got here.
I...I'm in no rush.

569
00:23:04,960 --> 00:23:06,240
Oh, oh, oh.

570
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:07,200
Are you dizzy from the drinks...

571
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:08,360
or from that creeping dance
move I just taught you?

572
00:23:08,360 --> 00:23:10,080
Oh, probably both.

573
00:23:10,080 --> 00:23:11,920
I think I’d better head home now.

574
00:23:11,920 --> 00:23:12,720
I'll give you a ride.

575
00:23:12,720 --> 00:23:13,840
It's fine, really. No need.

576
00:23:13,840 --> 00:23:14,760
Come on, I'll go send you off.

577
00:23:14,760 --> 00:23:16,520
No, really, it's fine!

578
00:23:18,520 --> 00:23:19,520
Are you okay?

579
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:26,400
Whoa!

580
00:23:27,800 --> 00:23:29,040
Wait, where the hell did they go?

581
00:23:35,120 --> 00:23:39,080
This is where I used to work.

582
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:41,720
Pretty high-class, isn't it?

583
00:23:41,720 --> 00:23:42,640
Totally.

584
00:23:42,640 --> 00:23:45,680
I used to be a flight attendant,
you know.

585
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:47,440
But this place actually
has some local lore.

586
00:23:47,440 --> 00:23:49,200
Ghost stories.

587
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:50,040
Do you want to hear one?

588
00:23:50,040 --> 00:23:50,920
Yeah.

589
00:23:51,160 --> 00:23:52,560
Alright, if you want to hear it,
come film this first.

590
00:23:52,560 --> 00:23:54,120
Let's go find a spot to sit
and I'll tell you.

591
00:23:54,120 --> 00:23:55,560
Shall we sit here?

592
00:23:55,800 --> 00:23:57,040
Ahhh!

593
00:23:57,040 --> 00:23:58,040
I haven't even started
telling the story yet,

594
00:23:58,040 --> 00:23:59,120
you scared the crap out of me!

595
00:23:59,440 --> 00:24:00,560
What?

596
00:24:02,760 --> 00:24:03,640
You absolute nuisances.

597
00:24:03,640 --> 00:24:05,160
No matter where I run,
I just can't escape you guys.

598
00:24:05,160 --> 00:24:06,400
Sky.

599
00:24:06,400 --> 00:24:08,720
What the hell are you
doing here all by yourself?

600
00:24:08,720 --> 00:24:10,600
Don't tell me you're
thinking of ending it all?

601
00:24:10,600 --> 00:24:12,080
I should be asking you that instead.

602
00:24:12,080 --> 00:24:13,280
How did you even get in here?

603
00:24:13,280 --> 00:24:14,440
Didn't you already resign?

604
00:24:14,440 --> 00:24:16,520
Well, I still have the keys,
obviously.

605
00:24:16,520 --> 00:24:17,640
Hey, how about this?

606
00:24:17,640 --> 00:24:19,120
Can you play a ghost
for me for a bit?

607
00:24:19,120 --> 00:24:20,160
Can you do a "Haunting Me" vibe?

608
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:21,200
Sounds interesting.

609
00:24:21,200 --> 00:24:23,560
A cannibalistic ghost seems
to suit your friend perfectly, Chaba.

610
00:24:23,560 --> 00:24:24,200
You down?

611
00:24:24,200 --> 00:24:26,400
Enough.
Go play it yourself.

612
00:24:26,400 --> 00:24:27,920
You clout-chasing ghoul.

613
00:24:27,920 --> 00:24:29,600
You ungrateful,
snobbish ghost.

614
00:24:29,600 --> 00:24:31,120
I'm not playing along
with you, Chaba.

615
00:24:31,120 --> 00:24:32,280
Why the hell are you
so mad at me?

616
00:24:32,280 --> 00:24:33,520
I'm trying to get you
into the spotlight here.

617
00:24:33,520 --> 00:24:35,040
If you blow up,

618
00:24:35,040 --> 00:24:36,400
you'll get a side income,
you know.

619
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:37,960
Mind your own business.

620
00:24:37,960 --> 00:24:40,120
I don't want to be friends
with you anymore.

621
00:24:43,920 --> 00:24:45,360
You country bumpkin.

622
00:24:45,360 --> 00:24:46,560
Where the hell have
you been hiding?

623
00:24:46,560 --> 00:24:48,360
Why didn't you show up to do
the livestream at Yeppy Clinic?

624
00:24:48,360 --> 00:24:50,280
Listen here,
you jackass doctor.

625
00:24:50,280 --> 00:24:51,880
What the hell is
your problem with me?

626
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:52,880
Have you still not stopped using that...

627
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:54,520
GPS tracker to follow me around?

628
00:24:54,520 --> 00:24:55,880
Fans, go home.

629
00:24:55,880 --> 00:24:57,600
We're gonna talk in private.

630
00:24:57,600 --> 00:24:59,840
Go. Take the lights
with you too.

631
00:24:59,840 --> 00:25:02,040
Look, Doctor,
I'm asking you seriously.

632
00:25:02,040 --> 00:25:04,640
Why are you so obsessed with me?
Huh?

633
00:25:04,640 --> 00:25:06,800
If you like me that much,
go get in line.

634
00:25:06,800 --> 00:25:08,480
Chaba.

635
00:25:08,480 --> 00:25:10,440
Can you really not tell at all?

636
00:25:10,440 --> 00:25:13,960
Of course I can, that's why
I told you to go get in line.

637
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:16,440
No. Can you really not see...

638
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:18,080
that I'm a handsome guy?

639
00:25:19,360 --> 00:25:21,960
Look at my eyes.
I look just like Nam Joo-hyuk.

640
00:25:22,680 --> 00:25:25,520
I look like the male lead
from that Chinese jade drama.

641
00:25:25,520 --> 00:25:29,040
The only jade you look
like is green noodles.

642
00:25:29,040 --> 00:25:29,960
Chaba.

643
00:25:29,960 --> 00:25:30,600
What?

644
00:25:30,600 --> 00:25:32,040
You're so full of yourself.

645
00:25:32,040 --> 00:25:33,000
Listen to me.

646
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:34,120
Let me tell you something.

647
00:25:34,120 --> 00:25:36,040
Right now, you've reached a point

648
00:25:36,040 --> 00:25:37,640
where nobody can warn you anymore.

649
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:38,760
Do you even realize that?

650
00:25:38,760 --> 00:25:40,280
Let me tell you something, Doctor.

651
00:25:40,280 --> 00:25:43,240
That exact person is you.

652
00:25:43,240 --> 00:25:45,480
Please leave Glamorous Airline
immediately. I'm scared.

653
00:25:45,480 --> 00:25:46,480
Security!

654
00:25:47,120 --> 00:25:48,120
Security!

655
00:25:49,520 --> 00:25:50,520
Security!

656
00:25:52,720 --> 00:25:53,720
Get out!

657
00:26:04,040 --> 00:26:06,040
Come on in, please.

658
00:26:11,160 --> 00:26:13,880
Your tattoo is so cool.

659
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:14,840
You can touch it.

660
00:26:14,960 --> 00:26:16,160
Can I?

661
00:26:16,160 --> 00:26:16,920
Sure.

662
00:26:16,920 --> 00:26:18,880
Oh!

663
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:21,200
And why haven't you
taken off your mask yet?

664
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:22,720
Why are you speaking
with "Ka"?

665
00:26:25,120 --> 00:26:28,040
Well, sometimes
when I'm at home...

666
00:26:28,040 --> 00:26:29,520
I tend to act a bit girly.

667
00:26:30,600 --> 00:26:32,320
That's totally fine.
It's actually quite cute.

668
00:26:32,320 --> 00:26:33,000
The reason I haven't
taken off my mask is

669
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:33,640
because I feel like...

670
00:26:33,640 --> 00:26:34,760
I only want to take it off for

671
00:26:34,760 --> 00:26:35,760
someone I truly open my heart to.

672
00:26:37,800 --> 00:26:39,200
I'll let him eat
some mushrooms.

673
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:41,360
Otherwise,
he'll find out I'm a chick.

674
00:26:41,720 --> 00:26:45,280
And maybe it'll get him
to open his heart to me.

675
00:26:46,720 --> 00:26:47,600
Hold on a second.

676
00:26:51,280 --> 00:26:53,280
If you want to open your heart
to someone...

677
00:26:53,280 --> 00:26:55,840
you should try
this Bear-Eared Mushroom.

678
00:26:55,840 --> 00:26:57,320
I guarantee...

679
00:26:57,320 --> 00:27:00,440
you will get a taste
of something entirely new.

680
00:27:00,440 --> 00:27:02,160
You've got so
many tricks up your sleeve.

681
00:27:02,160 --> 00:27:04,160
Just one bite is fine.

682
00:27:09,720 --> 00:27:11,400
Aren't you going to eat some?

683
00:27:11,400 --> 00:27:12,360
Let's eat together.

684
00:27:12,360 --> 00:27:14,760
Just...just one bite then.

685
00:27:14,760 --> 00:27:17,520
Now we're talking.

686
00:27:17,520 --> 00:27:19,720
I can feel Nirvana.

687
00:27:23,440 --> 00:27:25,440
Shit, I'm so high.

688
00:27:25,440 --> 00:27:26,800
Can I touch you?

689
00:27:26,800 --> 00:27:28,480
Can I crawl
my fingers on you?

690
00:27:31,200 --> 00:27:32,080
This is absolutely amazing.

691
00:27:32,080 --> 00:27:32,720
There's some on this side too.

692
00:27:32,720 --> 00:27:36,720
Oh, let me crawl
on the other side too.

693
00:27:40,160 --> 00:27:41,440
I'm so shy.

694
00:27:41,440 --> 00:27:43,640
I'm blushing all over.

695
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:45,960
You look so natural doing that.

696
00:27:46,840 --> 00:27:50,000
How did both of my targets...

697
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:52,600
end up waiting for me
right here at home?

698
00:27:52,600 --> 00:27:55,360
I'm waiting.
Waiting for your best move.

699
00:28:01,880 --> 00:28:04,800
Can you do it harder than this?

700
00:28:04,800 --> 00:28:06,040
I can't take this anymore.

701
00:28:11,040 --> 00:28:12,040
Mr. Mask...

702
00:28:27,000 --> 00:28:28,640
can you go harder than this?

703
00:28:28,640 --> 00:28:31,160
I can't take it anymore.
I love it.

704
00:28:31,160 --> 00:28:31,760
Turn it up!
More, more!

705
00:28:45,520 --> 00:28:46,520
Hey!

706
00:28:48,600 --> 00:28:49,600
Chai!

707
00:28:55,560 --> 00:28:56,720
Shit!

708
00:28:56,720 --> 00:28:57,840
Ninja!

709
00:28:57,840 --> 00:28:59,320
Chai!

710
00:29:02,080 --> 00:29:05,560
Wait, you two know each other?

711
00:29:05,560 --> 00:29:07,560
- He's an ex.
- He's an ex.

712
00:29:12,720 --> 00:29:14,680
What is it with Thai people and their exes?

713
00:29:28,720 --> 00:29:30,840
Well, a female friend of mine...

714
00:29:30,840 --> 00:29:36,760
accidentally ended up
sleeping with her gay friend...

715
00:29:36,760 --> 00:29:40,800
And your friend
who slept with a gay guy...

716
00:29:41,280 --> 00:29:42,480
was it on the island?

717
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:43,120
No.

718
00:29:43,120 --> 00:29:44,080
Yeah, yeah!

719
00:29:44,080 --> 00:29:45,080
Oh, yes, yes!

720
00:29:46,560 --> 00:29:48,320
I think for this case...

721
00:29:48,320 --> 00:29:51,320
it has to be an eye for an eye.

722
00:29:51,320 --> 00:29:52,080
Gay against gay!

723
00:29:52,080 --> 00:29:53,280
Yeah.

724
00:29:55,320 --> 00:29:58,080
Hey, hey! I wanted
to say "an eye for an eye"!

725
00:29:58,080 --> 00:29:59,320
Okay, sorry!

726
00:29:59,840 --> 00:30:01,920
You mark my words...

727
00:30:01,920 --> 00:30:07,920
Tid-Gift will never be
Chai's victim ever again!

728
00:30:12,400 --> 00:30:13,400
Do you want some water?

729
00:30:14,960 --> 00:30:16,680
You need to change
your name from Tid-Gift.

730
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:18,240
Yeah.

731
00:30:18,240 --> 00:30:19,200
What should the name be?

732
00:30:19,200 --> 00:30:19,960
Gift-Phong?

733
00:30:19,960 --> 00:30:21,720
That sounds pretty close to mine.

734
00:30:21,720 --> 00:30:22,840
Gift-Den?

735
00:30:22,840 --> 00:30:23,280
Sounds a bit Western.

736
00:30:23,280 --> 00:30:23,600
Gift-Koff?

737
00:30:23,880 --> 00:30:24,440
Gift-Koff?

738
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:25,400
Yeah, how's that?

739
00:30:25,400 --> 00:30:26,080
A bit strange, isn't it?

740
00:30:26,080 --> 00:30:26,880
Gift-*?

741
00:30:26,880 --> 00:30:27,640
Oh!

742
00:30:27,640 --> 00:30:28,320
Gift-*just like that?

743
00:30:28,320 --> 00:30:29,400
Does it pinch?

744
00:30:29,400 --> 00:30:31,200
Like a clip or something?

745
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:32,960
And what do we say next?

746
00:30:33,480 --> 00:30:33,680
Gift-Boy.

747
00:30:33,840 --> 00:30:34,120
Gift-Boy.

748
00:30:34,560 --> 00:30:35,320
Gift-Boy.

749
00:30:35,320 --> 00:30:35,920
Oh!

750
00:30:36,360 --> 00:30:37,960
You clout-chasing ghoul.

751
00:30:37,960 --> 00:30:39,280
You ungrateful,
snobbish ghost.

752
00:30:39,280 --> 00:30:42,000
I don't want to be
friends with you anymore.

753
00:30:42,000 --> 00:30:42,960
Dumbass!

754
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:43,800
You country bumpkin.

755
00:30:43,800 --> 00:30:44,400
Wait.

756
00:30:44,400 --> 00:30:45,600
Where the hell
have you been hiding?

757
00:30:45,600 --> 00:30:47,320
Why didn't you show up to do
the livestream at Yeppy Clinic?

758
00:30:47,320 --> 00:30:48,000
Let's do it again.

759
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:48,600
Editing the take.

760
00:30:48,600 --> 00:30:49,440
Doctor, please step back a bit.

761
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:51,080
We'll hold the camera
on the Doctor, okay?

762
00:30:51,080 --> 00:30:51,800
Camera holding on the Doctor.

763
00:30:51,800 --> 00:30:53,800
Why the hell am I
getting cursed out so much?

764
00:30:53,800 --> 00:30:55,440
Getting insulted
from all directions here!

765
00:30:55,440 --> 00:30:57,600
Today, Eight-Sided Mirror...

766
00:30:57,600 --> 00:30:59,440
presents...

767
00:30:59,440 --> 00:31:01,200
That person was
totally blocking me!

768
00:31:01,200 --> 00:31:03,920
Mirror...Sorry!

769
00:31:03,920 --> 00:31:08,120
Three, two, one... Gay!

770
00:31:08,120 --> 00:31:10,040
Listen,

771
00:31:10,040 --> 00:31:11,240
sweeties...

772
00:31:11,240 --> 00:31:14,920
are you two straight guys
trying to crash the party?

773
00:31:14,920 --> 00:31:16,360
Uh...

774
00:31:16,360 --> 00:31:17,520
Hello, hi!

775
00:31:17,520 --> 00:31:18,120
Sorry!

776
00:31:19,200 --> 00:31:20,520
Turn it up!

777
00:31:20,520 --> 00:31:21,320
Turn it up! Go ahead!

778
00:31:32,760 --> 00:31:35,440
Turn it up!
More, more!

779
00:31:35,440 --> 00:31:36,400
From the side!

780
00:31:36,400 --> 00:31:37,080
Right from the side!

781
00:31:37,080 --> 00:31:38,080
Come do it yourself!

782
00:31:38,680 --> 00:31:40,120
My neck almost snapped just now.

783
00:31:41,040 --> 00:31:43,560
That was so bad earlier, so bad.

784
00:31:44,080 --> 00:31:44,720
Take it back!

785
00:31:44,720 --> 00:31:45,280
What the hell?

786
00:31:45,280 --> 00:31:46,360
Just take your damn things back!

787
00:31:46,360 --> 00:31:47,880
What on earth is happening here?

788
00:31:47,880 --> 00:31:50,160
Have you ever had a friend
secretly sleep with your ex?

789
00:31:50,160 --> 00:31:51,560
Even if he's my ex...

790
00:31:51,560 --> 00:31:53,560
you still have no right
to mess with him!

791
00:32:00,840 --> 00:32:01,040
Huh?

792
00:32:01,240 --> 00:32:01,440
Hey!

793
00:32:01,560 --> 00:32:03,040
Hey!

794
00:32:03,240 --> 00:32:04,360
Oh, enough!

795
00:32:04,360 --> 00:32:05,440
Explain this to me.
Who is this?

796
00:32:05,440 --> 00:32:06,320
I don't know him.

797
00:32:06,320 --> 00:32:07,600
But I've seen this engineer before...

798
00:32:07,600 --> 00:32:08,800
acting all sketchy on the plane.

799
00:32:08,800 --> 00:32:09,800
Could he be an assassin?

800
00:32:11,480 --> 00:32:12,440
I knew it!

801
00:32:12,480 --> 00:32:14,480
You must be one of them.

802
00:32:14,840 --> 00:32:15,480
Sky!

803
00:32:15,480 --> 00:32:16,480
No need to mourn...

804
00:32:16,480 --> 00:32:18,520
because you'll be next.
